    AlternateItemInput

    public class AlternateInput<T>
extends ParseMultiInput<T,Input<T>>
    An alternateInput is a MultiInput consisting of several different inputs of the same type. Each sub-input is optional and the first input with a value is taken This is for implementing a pull-down of common options with a text-box for general input.
